data.description: Price Improvement! Move in ready! Motivated Seller to credit 10,000.00 that can be used towards home upgrades, closing costs or to buy down points! This home is in a beautiful country setting that sits way off the road for that perfect homestead with No restrictions. Fully Fenced so bring your horses (horse run area in back of the barn), goats, sheep and chickens. There is a garden area, above ground pool, and with over 7 acres there is plenty of room to roam and grow. The owners have added on to the original home making an additional 2 car attached garage, on top of the detached 4 car shop. They have added a primary suite, office and bonus room with another bathroom. The owner is still working on finishes, but you can come in and make this one your own as all the major stuff is done. NEW roof, NEW windows, NEW HVAC units, NEW flooring and paint inside and out. NEW field lines for septic, NEW porch, NEW kitchen and bathrooms. Don’t miss your chance to make this home your own!
